<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>About DIHAX</h2>
      <p>Your trusted partner for cybersecurity and IT infrastructure</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-main">
        <p class="about-intro">DIHAX is a Canadian cybersecurity and IT services company bringing together experienced professionals dedicated to protecting and empowering clients worldwide.</p>
        <p class="about-description">Our expertise spans mobile security, web application testing, reverse engineering, and comprehensive IT infrastructure management. With over 10 years of combined experience, we deliver enterprise-grade security and support to organizations and individuals alike.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="expertise-grid">
        <div class="expertise-item">
          <h4>Cybersecurity Expertise</h4>
          <p>Advanced cybersecurity expertise with specialized certifications in penetration testing, mobile security, and malware analysis. Our team excels in identifying vulnerabilities before they become threats.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="expertise-item">
          <h4>IT Infrastructure</h4>
          <p>Over a decade of hands-on experience in networking, system administration, and IT support. Microsoft certified professionals ready to optimize your technology infrastructure.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="expertise-item">
          <h4>Development Background</h4>
          <p>Deep technical knowledge in mobile and web development enables us to understand systems from the ground up, providing more thorough security assessments and IT solutions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

